<H3> <TI>   Police Brigadier General Killed in Asyut </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0602203194 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2000 GMT 6 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0602203194 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Asyut, 6 Feb (MENA)--Police Brigadier General 'Umar 
Hasan Mustafa, assistant director to the northern Suhaj security 
division, was martyred in Asyut this evening. 
  Unidentified gunmen opened fire at Brig. Gen. Mustafa as he 
was leaving his home near al-Jumhuriyah Street in Asyut. He was 
killed instantly. The gunmen managed to escape. Security 
forces cordoned off the area and instituted a search for the 
criminals. Asyut authorities are investigating the incident. 

</TEXT>

