  [Text] In Assam, the officer in charge of the Gopur Police 
Station of Sunitpur District was killed in a bomb explosion last 
night. Another person received serious injuries. Police 
sources at Guwahati said that the suspected ULFA [United 
Liberation Front of Assam] militants planted the bomb under the 
