Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A military spokesman for the General Command of the 
al-'Asifah Forces -- the command of the Fatah forces inside the 
occupied territories -- has stated the following: 
  Our cells operating inside the occupied homeland have 
planted 
advanced explosive charges in the Haifa chemical factory north 
of the industrial zone, which is adjacent to the Haifa oil 
