<H3> <TI>   Further on Investigations Into Cinema Bombings </TI></H3>
<H4>   Minister Discloses Sabotage, Arrests </H4>
<F P=102> JN0902132494 Amman Radio Jordan Network in Arabic 1200 GMT 9 
