<F P=101> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Unidentified Assailants Wound DEP Secretary General </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0602150394 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1445 GMT 6 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA0602150394 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Istanbul, Feb 6 (AA) -- Unidentified gunmen shot 
and slightly wounded Murat Bozlak, secretary general of the 
Democracy Party (DEP). 
  AA was told that Bozlak was hit by four bullets in Kecioren 
District after midnight. Police said the assailants fled. 
  Hospital officials said Bozlak was in good condition and 
recovering from his wounds. 
  No one immediately claimed responsibility for the attack. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

