<H3> <TI>   La Paz District Attorney's Office Bombed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY0502170794 La Paz Television Nacional Network in Spanish 
0100 GMT 5 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY0502170794 </F>
<F P=104>  La Paz Television Nacional Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] The La Paz district attorney's office has been 
damaged by a terrorist attack. 
  An explosion shook the La Paz district attorney's office at 
noon today. The explosion occurred in a restricted area very 
close to Prosecutor Javier Dibs's office. The damage was small 
and no one was injured. [passage omitted] 
  The bomb was placed in a corridor through which Dibs enters 
and leaves his office. [passage omitted] 
  Two weeks ago the Ministry of Government withdrew the police 
who were guarding the office. It is expected that the new order 
assigning officers to different posts will resolve the problem. 

</TEXT>

