its internal affairs. Syria's independent stance is clear to 
all. 
  On the presence of Palestinian forces opposed to the 
Gaza-Jericho Accord in Damascus, the Syrian ambassador said: We 
believe that those who fight to liberate their territory are not 
terrorists. They are merely struggling to liberate their usurped 
land. [passage omitted] 

