<F P=106> [Report by army affairs correspondent Karmela Menashe] </F>
  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] Military and political sources 
say that a trend of escalating terror attacks has persisted 
since the beginning of the dialogue with the PLO. In 1993, the 
number of terror attacks in Lebanon doubled, the number of 
