1911, pp 10-11. 
  31. Ibid., p 159. 
  32. "Manual for French Army Senior Troop Commanders," St. 
Petersburg, 1914, p 54. 
  33. See VOYENNO-ISTORICHESKIY ZHURNAL, No 11, 1984, p 73. 
  34. See "Istoriya voyennogo iskusstva," Vol 1, pp 162-163. 
  35. See "Mirovaya voyna v tsifrakh" [World War in Figures], 
